                        <span class="faq-question">How do you handle complex B2B SaaS products?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">Complexity is our specialty. We've successfully simplified numerous complex B2B SaaS products through our systematic approach. Our fresh perspective often reveals simplification opportunities that internal teams miss, leading to more intuitive user experiences.</p>
                </div>
