                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">We maintain a lean team structure where each designer handles 2-3 projects maximum. This ensures dedicated attention to your project while maintaining flexibility for urgent needs. We never overcommit our resources, guaranteeing consistent quality and availability.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
                 <div class="faq-item">
