                        <span class="faq-question">What's your satisfaction guarantee?</span>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="faq-answer">We offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee - if you're not completely satisfied, you don't pay. Our iterative approach includes regular checkpoints and feedback loops, ensuring we stay aligned with your vision and deliver exceptional results.</p>
                </div>
